       </para>
      </entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry>
       <para>
        <option>style</option>
       </para>
      </entry>
      <entry>
       <para>
        The font style, such as <literal>Medium</literal>,
        <literal>Regular</literal>, <literal>Bold</literal>,
